        <p>Welcome to the Poker Recording site. It's a full setup for recording a home poker game.</p>
        <p>This combines some IoT devices to scan RFID stickers on a pack of cards and send them to an API.</p>

        <p>Place a playing card (with an RFID/NFC sticker) on an RFID/NFC reader, this will send a request to this API with the value A♥ (♣♦♠) and the position - Player or board. This will then update the picture on disc to the correct image, this in turn is already an Image (or Media Source) control in an OBS Scene, so will update to the given image.</p>
